{
  "stem": "3331.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, my father was managing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were-- there changed a lot that year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, for instance, the official-- the leaders of the Polish government started-- see, so long as Pilsudski was marshal-- Jozef Pilsudski-- the Jews didn't feel so much antisemitism, because he was very good for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He believed in the ethnic groups in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The minute he died, everything changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He died in March-- in March or May, 1935.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since he died, a general by the name of Rydz-Smigly took over, and the whole situation changed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of-- right away, the head of the Polish church, which was a Cardinal Hlond-- this cardinal came out, officially, and he said, we have, in Poland, three and a half a million Jews.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Definitely, three million are too many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from the three million, a half a million we could survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jozef Beck, who was the Secretary of State-- the foreign minister-- had a speech.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In this speech he said, we have to get rid of three million Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We cannot allow to have three million Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Officially they said it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a prime minister-- his name was Skladkowski.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this prime minister-- there were some groups, and they said, we have to beat the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he said, we have-- we-- we don't have to kill them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We don't have to beat them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we have to get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Economically, first, and then later physically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to call this Skladkowski Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Owszem. 'Owszem,' in Poland, means 'by all means.' Because he, in the Senate, had a speech, and he said, if you speak about hooliganism, I am against it.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
